@startuml
!include ../um-theme.puml

title libtea — Package Overview

left to right direction

package "libtea::ml" as ML {
  [Estimator] as Estimator
  [LinearRegression] as LinearRegression
  [linear_regression.cpp\n(implementation)] as LRImpl
  [metrics.hpp\n(mae, mse, r2_score)] as Metrics
  [train_test_split.hpp\n(train_test_split, SplitData)] as Split
  [base.hpp\n(Vector, Matrix)] as Types
  [SplitData] as SplitData
}

[examples/basic_usage.cpp] as Example

Example --> Split : calls
Example --> LinearRegression : uses
Example --> Metrics : calls

LinearRegression ..|> Estimator
LinearRegression --> Types : uses
LinearRegression ..> LRImpl : defined in
Metrics --> Types : uses Vector
Split --> Types : uses Vector/Matrix
Split --> SplitData : returns

note right of LinearRegression
  LinearRegression stores
  mean/stddev from fit()
  and reuses them in predict().
end note

@enduml
